He's as chubby

583
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:17,590
as I was when I was little.

584
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,520
My son's birthday is coming.

585
00:35:20,150 --> 00:35:21,750
He asked me to buy him a plane.

586
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,480
That little brat.

587
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:28,400
Today was my son's first time performing on the stage.

588
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,630
He wet his pants.

589
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,320
Useless kid.

590
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:33,030
My son is going to school.

591
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:34,960
His mom and I invited a Wenquxing for him.

592
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,800
I hope he can study hard.

593
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,210
My son's teacher

594
00:35:39,310 --> 00:35:41,190
called me to the school again today.

595
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:42,320
I couldn't hold back

596
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:44,400
and beat him up when I came back.

597
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:48,190
I regretted it immediately.

598
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:49,280
Will he hate me

599
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:51,670
when he grows up?

600
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:53,800
My son wishes

601
00:35:54,030 --> 00:35:56,690
to marry Miaomiao in the future on his birthday.

602
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,550
Good for him.

603
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,660
May his wish come true.

604
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:04,480
God,

605
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,280
can I exchange my life

606
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,030
for my son's?

607
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,600
I can't bear to leave you two.

608
00:36:34,710 --> 00:36:35,510
I also can't bear to leave

609
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:36,840
my friends.

610
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:43,920
Hu.

611
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,880
You must visit Hong Kong once

612
00:36:46,590 --> 00:36:47,150
and take a photo of

613
00:36:47,150 --> 00:36:48,710
Central Crossroads for me.

614
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,110
Xiaowa,

615
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:51,760
do you remember?

616
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,480
The task I gave you

617
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:56,230
when I went to see you?

618
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,670
During the time I'm not here,

619
00:36:58,670 --> 00:36:59,440
you must help me

620
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,550
take good care of them,

621
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:01,810
especially Miaomiao.

622
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:02,920
Discipline her.

623
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:04,480
I hope

624
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,670
that when I come back from Beijing,

625
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:07,880
she can appear in front of me

626
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,070
with a new look.

627
00:37:09,630 --> 00:37:11,360
This is the task I'm giving you.

628
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,150
Yaya,

629
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:14,920
take good care of your sister for me.

630
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:17,000
Shanqing will be fine.

631
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,100
I'll bless her for you.

632
00:37:21,550 --> 00:37:22,350
Miaomiao,

633
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,890
you're scared, aren't you?

634
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:29,410
You cried a lot, right?

635
00:37:34,510 --> 00:37:37,440
You're finally afraid that I might leave you, right?

636
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:39,760
I've only ever had one wish

637
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,030
since childhood.

638
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,670
To marry you when I grow up.

639
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,360
I have to break my promise this time.

640
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:48,230
I can't accompany you

641
00:37:48,230 --> 00:37:49,840
to the places you want to go.

642
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,110
I also can't marry you.

643
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,150
But remember,

644
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:56,920
in this lifetime,

645
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:58,180
you'll always have me.

646
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,030
When I'm alive, I can beat up

647
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,550
anyone who bullies you.

648
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,150
When I'm dead,

649
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,440
if anyone dares to bully you,

650
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,030
I'll haunt them as a ghost.

651
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:23,190
I'm taking this bell with me.

652
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:14,880
This is the first time I'm worshiping you.

653
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,190
If...

654
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:20,740
there really were gods in this world,

655
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,280
please

656
00:39:29,030 --> 00:39:31,000
bless my parents.

657
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:35,440
Since God

658
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:36,880
has given me this fate,

659
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,710
it's no big deal.

660
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:40,670
It's just leaving a bit earlier.

661
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,480
My illness

662
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,480
can't be cured.

663
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,360
But I won't

664
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,630
accept this fate.

665
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,070
I want to decide

666
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,800
when I leave this world myself.

667
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:55,240
I don't want you to

668
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:57,150
see me tortured by illness,

669
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,550
and I don't want everyone

670
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,840
to cry for me.

671
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,880
That's not like me.

672
00:40:04,030 --> 00:40:07,030
Dad, Mom, my friends,

673
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,510
uncles, aunties,

674
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:10,920
Baoshan, and Fang,

675
00:40:12,230 --> 00:40:13,000
please remember me

676
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,880
as carefree and untroubled.

677
00:40:16,070 --> 00:40:17,400
Don't be sad, everyone.

678
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,000
Let's just

679
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,880
say goodbye happily.

680
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,370
I love you all...

681
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:34,360
forever.

682
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:54,550
Go to my place to eat ribs.

683
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:56,030
My dad's already made them.

684
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:57,400
I don't want to eat!

685
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:58,840
Come on.

686
00:40:58,840 --> 00:41:00,510
My mom's waiting for me to grill fish at home.

687
00:41:00,510 --> 00:41:01,150
I'm off.

688
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,120
Cheng Miaomiao!

689
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,580
Next time, I'll come for ribs.

690
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:38,590
If...

691
00:41:40,190 --> 00:41:42,280
time could be rewound,

692
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,280
I wish

693
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:46,010
none of this had ever happened.

694
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:47,550
If...

695
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:50,730
there really were gods in this world,

696
00:41:52,030 --> 00:41:54,030
I'd hope that you'd bless Li Si

697
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:56,070
so that in another world,

698
00:41:56,070 --> 00:41:57,880
he'd never get angry again.

699
00:41:58,510 --> 00:41:59,320
If...

700
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:02,960
Couldn't we have just

701
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:05,030
stayed in the oilfield forever

702
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,590
and never been apart?

703
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:20,240
Yuan Shanqing's killing Yuan Yong

704
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,200
was ultimately ruled as self-defense.

705
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:25,110
The day she was released,

706
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,530
Yaya went early to wait for her.

707
00:42:28,710 --> 00:42:30,240
In this bittersweet story,

708
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:32,830
no one treated our youth kindly.

709
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:34,920
We had

710
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:37,610
a farewell that was far from complete.

711
00:42:38,710 --> 00:42:39,360
We all thought

712
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:41,760
that we'd become great people when we grew up.

713
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:43,290
But before we could grow up,

714
00:42:43,440 --> 00:42:44,630
life's harshness

715
00:42:44,630 --> 00:42:45,880
caught us off guard.

716
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,230
I remember

717
00:42:49,230 --> 00:42:50,760
every event from that year.

718
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:53,670
Remember every face from my youth.

719
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:56,320
Li Si...

720
00:42:57,670 --> 00:42:58,670
Li Si is gone.

721
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:00,670
And with him...

722
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:04,960
our youth ended.
